<h3 id="ingredients">Ingredients</h3>

<ul>
  <li>2 medium ripe bananas, mashed</li>
  <li>1 cup of uncooked quick oats*</li>
  <li>1/4 cup crushed walnuts</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="instructions">Instructions</h3>

<ol>
  <li>Preheat oven to 350°F. Spray a non-stick cookie sheet with cooking spray or use a Silpat.</li>
  <li>Combine the mashed bananas and oats in a bowl. Fold in the walnuts and place a tablespoon of each on the cookie sheet.</li>
  <li>Bake 15 minutes. Makes 16 cookies.</li>
  <li>Use gluten free oats such as Bob's Red Mill quick oats to make them gluten free. Adapted from the Burlap Bag .</li>
</ol>

